comment:
People say, "Oh, he is bad as her because he was in a toxic relationship". A Toxic Relationship doesn't mean both parties do equate acts. The best definition of a Toxic Relationship is this: 
"By definition, a toxic relationship is a relationship characterized by behaviours on the part of the toxic partner that are emotionally and, not infrequently, physically damaging to their partner. While a healthy relationship contributes to our self-esteem and emotional energy, a toxic relationship damages self-esteem and drains energy."

By that definition, where does it highlight EQUAL?  Not one bit. A toxic relationship can be stem from one side of a relationship, you do not need to be the cause of the conflicts and/or issues. TONS of people been in a toxic relationship, the question is how BAD was it. In JD's case, he was in a very bad toxic relationship where his ex-partner lied through her teeth and soul just to get her way. If Johnny is guilty of anything then he is guilty of marrying that idiot and that made him an idiot. BUT THAT'S IT. Nothing more than that. He deserves none of the things that he has received and, for that. AH needs to burn like the demon she really is for 90% of her lies has been 100% DEBUNKED and her history and screwing the Children at the CHLA cannot be ignored.
